    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >S.P.L.I.C.E.D.</h2>Take on the role of a strong-willed woman determined to challenge the tyranny of the mob leader Jiaolong and free Chinatown from their oppressor in this 3D side scroller action adventure, Metroidvania. Discover forgotten secrets and powerful weapons that will help you traverse the treacherous streets, as you set off on a dangerous mission to fight the mutants, monsters, and other enemies hiding within.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>3D Side-Scroller Action: </strong><br>Embark on a journey with beautifully crafted environments, mixing the depth of 3D landscapes with classic Metroidvania gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163220/extras/f8840c2e2692d51d7bfe35a8de9bd222.poster.avif?t=1687350306\" width=590 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163220/extras/f8840c2e2692d51d7bfe35a8de9bd222.webm?t=1687350306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163220/extras/f8840c2e2692d51d7bfe35a8de9bd222.mp4?t=1687350306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> <strong>Incredible Boss fight: </strong> <br>Prepare to test your skills against a colossal and menacing boss. Analyze patterns, exploit weaknesses and have your skills tested in this immersive fight.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163220/extras/56ca88e6ee66b9f745381a23c2ae9429.poster.avif?t=1687350306\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163220/extras/56ca88e6ee66b9f745381a23c2ae9429.webm?t=1687350306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163220/extras/56ca88e6ee66b9f745381a23c2ae9429.mp4?t=1687350306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> <strong>Exploration: </strong> <br>Beautiful scenery, hidden passages and charming backgrounds. Delve deep into this Biopunk Chinatown world as you try to uncover all of its secrets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163220/extras/59567e98182fc803cbabd542ca513ba6.poster.avif?t=1687350306\" width=768 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163220/extras/59567e98182fc803cbabd542ca513ba6.webm?t=1687350306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163220/extras/59567e98182fc803cbabd542ca513ba6.mp4?t=1687350306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><br><strong>Are you ready to face the oppressor? Your journey awaits in S.P.L.I.C.E.D., the definitive 3D side scroller Metroidvania adventure.</strong>",
